#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:46
msgid "Build Comment Moderation Suggestion"
msgstr "建立評論審核建議"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:47
msgid ""
"Reads one comment and builds a deterministic moderation suggestion without "
"writing."
msgstr "閱讀一則評論並建立確定性的審核建議，而不寫入。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:89
msgid "Compose Comment Moderation Result"
msgstr "撰寫評論 審核結果"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:90
msgid ""
"Composes one canonical comment moderation suggest/action result envelope."
msgstr "撰寫一個規範的評論審核建議/行動結果信封。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:128
msgid "Build Comment Mention Reply Suggestion"
msgstr "建立評論 提及 回覆 建議"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:129
msgid ""
"Detects a comment mention/followup trigger and prepares a reply suggestion "
"handoff without writing."
msgstr "偵測評論提及/後續觸發並準備回覆建議移交，而不寫入。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:159
msgid "Read Comment Trigger Queue"
msgstr "閱讀評論觸發隊列"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:160
msgid ""
"Reads existing comments and builds a trigger candidate queue without writing."
msgstr "讀取現有評論並建立觸發器候選隊列，而無需寫入。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:193
msgid "Get Comment Queue Health"
msgstr "取得評論隊列健康狀況"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:194
msgid ""
"Reads a bounded comment queue and summarizes moderation, reply, and "
"escalation health without writing."
msgstr "讀取有界評論佇列並總結審核、回覆和升級健康狀況，而無需寫入。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:222
msgid "Get Comment Action Priority Queue"
msgstr "取得評論操作優先權佇列"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:223
msgid ""
"Reads a bounded comment queue and returns prioritized read-only moderation "
"and reply handoff candidates."
msgstr "讀取有界評論佇列並傳回優先的只讀審核和回復切換候選者。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:251
msgid "Get Comment Compliance Handoff"
msgstr "獲取評論 合規移交"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:252
msgid ""
"Aggregates comment queue health, action priority rows, and optional selected-"
"comment suggestions for host-side compliance workflows without writing."
msgstr "不寫入即可聚合評論佇列運行狀況、操作優先級行以及 host 端合規性工作流程的可選選定評論建議。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:284
msgid "Compose Comment Mention Reply Result"
msgstr "撰寫評論提及回覆結果"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:285
msgid ""
"Composes one canonical mention-triggered comment reply suggestion envelope."
msgstr "撰寫一個規範的提及觸發評論回覆建議信封。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:309
msgid "Build Comment Moderation Batch Suggestion"
msgstr "建構評論審核批量建議"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:310
msgid "Builds read-only moderation suggestions for a bounded list of comments."
msgstr "為有限的評論清單建立唯讀審核建議。"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:351
msgid "Compose Comment Moderation Batch Result"
msgstr "撰寫評論審核批次結果"

#: includes/Packages/Comment_Definitions/Core_Comment_Definitions.php:352
msgid ""
"Composes one canonical batch comment moderation suggestion result envelope."
msgstr "編寫一個標準的大量評論審核建議結果信封。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Comment_Package.php:56
msgid "WordPress Comment Abilities"
msgstr "WordPress 評論能力"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Comment_Package.php:57
msgid "Read-only comment moderation and reply helper abilities."
msgstr "只讀評論審核和回覆助手功能。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:55
#: includes/Packages/Core_Write_Package.php:55
msgid "WordPress Write Abilities"
msgstr "WordPress 寫入能力"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:56
msgid ""
"Host-governed WordPress write and destructive abilities with dry-run "
"previews and external approval."
msgstr "host 治理的 WordPress 寫入和破壞能力，具有 dry-run 預覽和外部批准。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:80
msgid "Delete Term"
msgstr "刪除術語"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:81
msgid ""
"Deletes a taxonomy term after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 核准後刪除分類項，或預設返回 dry-run 預覽。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:106
msgid "Merge Terms"
msgstr "合併條款"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:107
msgid ""
"Moves objects from source terms to a target term, then deletes source terms "
"after host approval."
msgstr "將物件從來源分類項移至目標分類項，然後在 host 核准後刪除來源分類項。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:142
msgid "Bulk Update Post Terms"
msgstr "大量更新貼文條款"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:143
msgid ""
"Bulk updates post or page taxonomy terms after host approval, with computed "
"dry-run previews and per-post before/after audit."
msgstr "在 host 核准後批量更新文章或頁面分類項，並提供計算的 dry-run 預覽和每個文章之前/之後的審核。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:242
msgid "Spam Comment"
msgstr "垃圾評論"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:243
msgid ""
"Marks one comment as spam after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview "
"by default."
msgstr "在 host 核准後將一則評論標記為垃圾郵件，或預設回傳 dry-run 預覽。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:259
msgid "Trash Comment"
msgstr "垃圾評論"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:260
msgid ""
"Moves one comment to trash after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview "
"by default."
msgstr "在 host 核准後將一則評論移至回收桶，或預設返回 dry-run 預覽。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:276
msgid "Delete Media Permanently"
msgstr "永久刪除媒體"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:277
msgid ""
"Permanently deletes one media attachment after host approval, or returns a "
"dry-run preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 核准後永久刪除一個媒體附件，或預設返回 dry-run 預覽。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:301
msgid "Trash Post"
msgstr "垃圾帖"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:302
msgid ""
"Moves one post to trash after host approval, or returns a dry-run preview by "
"default."
msgstr "在 host 核准後將一篇貼文移至回收桶，或預設返回 dry-run 預覽。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:325
msgid "Delete Post Permanently"
msgstr "永久刪除文章"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Destructive_Package.php:326
msgid ""
"Permanently deletes one post after host approval, or returns a dry-run "
"preview by default."
msgstr "在 host 核准後永久刪除一篇文章，或預設返回 dry-run 預覽。"

